{"tid":694128,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華加盟金融科技投行　擔任副主席","createTime":"2018-06-08T04:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T05:38:53.000Z","uid":150685,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"93ac3773d62f89a7a4cf06a44d6d60478564a40b","tid":694128,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/john-01_biO6A_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fjohn-01_biO6A_1200x0.png&h=f235a1c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》報道，前財政司司長曾俊華近日已加盟一家以金融科技為主的投資銀行Ion Pacific 擔任副主席。據南華引述該行表示，曾俊華多年來領導本港的經濟政策，料可協助該行發展。　<br />\n<br />\nIon Pacfifc 成立於2015年，是一家以以香港為基地的投資銀行，在英國倫敦及以色列特拉維夫設有辦事處。<br />\n<br />\n該行業務主要在亞洲、美國和以色列三地投資於科技項目。同時，該行擁有證監會發出的１、４、６及９號牌，即可從事證券交易、就證券提供意見、就機構融資提供意見及提供資產管理的業務。<br />\n<br />\n公司聯席首席執行官兼董事總經理 Itamar Har-Even 形容，曾俊華是香港成為領先金融中心的「前瞻思想者」，相信在他幫助下Ion Pacfifc 能夠為香港創科生態出一分力。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華2016年12月離開政府，之後競選特首，敗予現任特首林鄭月娥，由於曾俊華已經過了問責官員離職後的一年「冷河期」，今次加盟Ion Pacific ，毋須向政府申報。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華去年11月以主持身分為香港電台拍攝節目《香港故事》，開始在網上宣傳，廣播署長梁家榮曾收特首辦查詢，特首辦指曾未有申報，曾俊華稱反指沒有受薪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%81%8E%E5%86%B7%E6%B2%B3%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%8C%E5%BE%9E%E5%95%86-%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%8A%95%E8%A1%8C-%E6%93%94%E4%BB%BB%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%2586%25B7%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25BE%259E%25E5%2595%2586-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BF%258A%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%259B%259F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%2593%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F&d=akJa0BhxT1CBrAKZ%2F%2FudKQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=7c753a8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%2586%25B7%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25BE%259E%25E5%2595%2586-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BF%258A%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%259B%259F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%2593%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F&h=8f15ad25\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%81%8E%E5%86%B7%E6%B2%B3%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%8C%E5%BE%9E%E5%95%86-%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%8A%95%E8%A1%8C-%E6%93%94%E4%BB%BB%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD/</a>"},{"pid":"8e1324cffb852e9cc31a3a57d00efb981581f23c","tid":694128,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"唔做特首仲好"}]}